遥控器校准：Ensure that the trim sliders to the right and below the two sticks are in the center position.
Move both sticks in circles, then return them to the center position (the throttle should also be centered). Switch the autopilot mode switch on the top left between the two positions. Move the tuning knob on the top right fully clockwise and counterclockwise. With the control sticks centered, click on the ‘Ok’ and ‘Close’ buttons.

